'''飓风玛丽'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Marie}}）是有纪录以来第7强烈的[[太平洋飓风季|太平洋飓风]]，其[[气压|气压]]于2014年8月降至918[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，27.11[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）。系统源于8月10日离开非洲西海岸进入大西洋上空的一股[[东风波|东风波]]{{#tag:ref|[[东风波|东风波]]指的是沿[[信风|信风]]移动的倒置[[低压槽|低压槽]]<ref name="gloss">{{cite report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2013-03-25 | accessdate = 2015-03-27 | title = Glossary of NHC Terms | archivedate = 2014-06-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140601020814/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml}}</ref>。|group="注"}}，起初虽然组织结构有所改善，并且也有一些降雨和[[雷暴|雷暴]]活动，但很快就因干燥空气入侵而减弱。东风波在接下来几天里长途跋涉，先后穿越大西洋和[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]。8月19日，位于[[中美洲|中美洲]]以西的东风波内有[[低气压|低气压区]]整合。由于外界大气环境有利，系统周围的[[对流|对流]]活动和[[雨带|带状特征]]有所增长，到8月22日时已发展出足够的组织结构，在墨西哥[[阿卡普尔科|阿卡普尔科]]东南偏南方向约595公里海域成为第十三{{lang|en|E}}号热带低气压。低气压快速发展，仅形成6小时后风速就达到热带风暴强度，到8月23日又达到飓风标准。但由于受到部分[[风切变|垂直风切变]]影响，风暴的强化速度减缓，在[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]中的一级飓风强度下保持了一段时间。

8月24日，玛丽发展出[[风眼|风眼]]并[[快速增强|迅速强化]]成[[五级太平洋飓风列表|五级飓风]]，[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]达每小时260公里{{#tag:ref|如无特别说明，所有风速数据均为1分钟持续风速。|group="注"|name="winds"}}。处于最高强度期间，飓风的烈风强度风场范围有925公里宽。玛丽随后于8月25日开始[[眼墙置换|眼墙置换]]并因此逐渐减弱。接下来几天里，受行经洋面[[海面温度|水温]]降低、大气环境更加稳定的影响，风暴逐渐弱化至低于飓风强度标准。8月29日，系统中已没有深层对流组织迹象并退化成残留低气压。庞大的天气系统在随后几天里逐渐收缩，风速也在8月30日降至低于烈风强度。残留气旋最终失去原本层次分明的中心，于9月2日在[[夏威夷州|夏威夷州]]东北方向约1950公里洋面消散。

飓风玛丽的中心始终远离陆地，但由于风暴规模庞大，[[南加州|南加州]]到墨西哥西南部沿海地区的海浪高度都出现上升。[[洛斯卡沃斯|洛斯卡沃斯]]近海有3人在船只倾覆后溺亡。气旋的外围[[雨带|雨带]]给[[科利马州|科利马州]]和[[瓦哈卡州|瓦哈卡州]]带去暴雨，在当地引发洪灾，导致两人遇难。[[南下加利福尼亚州|南下加利福尼亚州]]也有类似灾情。8月末，玛丽给南加州带去数十年来最大规模的海浪。沿海地区受到3至4.6米的涌浪冲击，[[圣卡塔利娜岛|圣卡塔利娜岛]]和[[大洛杉矶地区|大洛杉矶地区]]都有建筑物受到结构性破坏。[[长滩_(加利福尼亚州)|长滩]]附近的一条防浪堤有部分被洪水突破，所受破坏估计价值达1000万美元。[[马利布_(加利福尼亚州)|马利布]]附近有1人溺毙。马利布有上百人因风暴而需救援，加上其他地区，救援作业有数百起之多，风暴一共造成的损失达到2000万美元。{{#tag:ref|所有货币数值如无特别说明，均指2014年[[美元|美元]]。|group="注"|name="damage"}}

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Marie 2014 track.png}}
2014年8月10日{{#tag:ref|如无特别说明，本条目中的所有日期和时间均为[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]。|group="注"}}，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]开始监控以[[经度|西经]]16°为中心、离开非洲西海岸进入大西洋向西移动的一股[[东风波|东风波]]<ref name="TCR">{{cite report | author = David A. Zelinski and Richard J. Pasch | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2015-01-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150212191450/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP132014_Marie.pdf | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Tropical Cyclone Report: Hurricane Marie | archivedate = 2015-02-12 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP132014_Marie.pdf | format = PDF | location = Miami, Florida}}</ref><ref>{{cite report | author = Mike Tichacek | work = Tropical Analysis Forecast Branch; National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2014-08-10 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2014/TWDAT.201408100603.txt | location = Miami, Florida | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140907173144/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2014/TWDAT.201408100603.txt | format = TXT | archivedate = 2014-09-07 | deadurl = no}}</ref>{{#tag:ref|[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]是东北太平洋（赤道以北、从[[中美洲|中美洲]]西海岸直至[[经度|西经]]140°之间的[[太平洋|太平洋]]）的[[区域专责气象中心|区域专责气象中心]]<ref>{{cite web | author = Christopher W. Landsea | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | year = 2014 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Subject: F1) What regions around the globe have tropical cyclones and who is responsible for forecasting there? | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/F1.html | archivedate = 2015-03-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150326101039/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/F1.html | deadurl = no}}</ref>。|group="注"|name="NHC"}}。由于[[对流|对流]]活动杂乱无章，系统不大可能得到迅速发展<ref>{{cite report | author = Eric S. Blake | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2014-08-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140907173127/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2014/TWOAT.201408100556.txt | archivedate = 2014-09-07 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | format = TXT | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2014/TWOAT.201408100556.txt}}</ref>。行进至非洲和[[佛得角|佛得角]]中途海域后，系统已形成大规模[[低气压|低气压区]]<ref>{{cite report | author = Stacy R. Stewart | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2014-08-10 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2014/TWOAT.201408101157.txt | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140907172110/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2014/TWOAT.201408101157.txt | archivedate = 2014-09-07 | deadurl = no | format = TXT}}</ref>。强度仍然微弱的系统内嵌在细长的[[低压槽|低压槽]]中<ref>{{cite report | author = Christopher W. Landsea | work = Tropical Analysis Forecast Branch; National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2014-08-10 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2014/TWDAT.201408102354.txt | location = Miami, Florida | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140907173153/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2014/TWDAT.201408102354.txt | archivedate = 2014-09-07 | deadurl = no | format = TXT}}</ref>，其中的对流很快便已消亡<ref>{{cite report | author = Eric S. Blake | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140907173201/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2014/TWOAT.201408110550.txt | date = 2014-08-11 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | archivedate = 2014-09-07 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2014/TWOAT.201408110550.txt | format = TXT}}</ref>。系统与[[季风槽|季风槽]]发生相互影响，于8月11日重新发展出降水和雷暴活动，覆盖了佛得角群岛西南方向大范围海域<ref>{{cite report | author = Christopher W. Landsea | work = Tropical Analysis Forecast Branch; National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2014-08-11 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2014/TWDAT.201408102354.txt | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140907173153/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2014/TWDAT.201408102354.txt | location = Miami, Florida | format = TXT | archivedate = 2014-09-07 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，但表面的低气压这时已经消散<ref>{{cite report | author = Mike Tichacek | work = Tropical Analysis Forecast Branch; National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2014-08-11 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2014/TWDAT.201408111102.txt | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140907172957/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2014/TWDAT.201408111102.txt | location = Miami, Florida | format = TXT | archivedate = 2014-09-07}}</ref>。由于外界环境中的空气较为干燥，美国国家飓风中心预计系统此后几天里都不会出现发展<ref>{{cite report | author = Eric S. Blake | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2014-08-11 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2014/TWOAT.201408112333.txt | format = TXT | archivedate = 2014-09-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140907173115/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2014/TWOAT.201408112333.txt}}</ref>。东风波继续向西穿越大西洋，于8月16日进入[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]<ref>{{cite report | author = Marshall K. Huffman | work = Tropical Analysis Forecast Branch; National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2014-08-16 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140907173125/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2014/TWDAT.201408160557.txt | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2014/TWDAT.201408160557.txt | location = Miami, Florida | format = TXT | archivedate = 2014-09-07}}</ref>。接下来系统继续与[[南美洲|南美大陆]]和[[冷心低压|上层低压槽]]相互影响，组织结构无法得到改善<ref name="TCR" />。

美国国家飓风中心预计，东太平洋的[[特万特佩克湾|特万特佩克湾]]以南方向洋面会在8月17日开始之后的5天内形成低气压区，并且有30%的可能发展出热带天气系统<ref>{{cite report | author = Eric S. Blake | date = 2014-08-17 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2014/TWOEP.201408172332.txt | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140904182202/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2014/TWOEP.201408172332.txt | format = TXT | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2014-09-04 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。8月18日，东风波已到达[[巴拿马|巴拿马]]上空，美国国家飓风中心将热带天气系统形成的可能性提升到60%<ref>{{cite report | author = Stacy R. Stewart | date = 2014-08-18 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | format = TXT | location = Miami, Florida | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140904182147/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2014/TWOEP.201408181727.txt | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2014/TWOEP.201408181727.txt | archivedate = 2014-09-04}}</ref>。东风波伴随着对流进入东太平洋<ref>{{cite report | author = Robbie J. Berg | date = 2014-08-18 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140904182158/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2014/TWOEP.201408190534.txt | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2014/TWOEP.201408190534.txt | format = TXT | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2014-09-04 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，于8月19日发展出低气压区。外界环境有利于进一步发展<ref>{{cite report | author = Stacy R. Stewart | date = 2014-08-19 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2014/TWOEP.201408192345.txt | format = TXT | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140904182124/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2014/TWOEP.201408192345.txt | deadurl = no | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2014-09-04}}</ref>，8月20日，雷暴活动已有所增长，结构也得到改善<ref>{{cite report | author = Stacy R. Stewart | date = 2014-08-20 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140904182121/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2014/TWOEP.201408202339.txt | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2014/TWOEP.201408202339.txt | format = TXT | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2014-09-04 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。系统中心层次分明，周围的[[雨带|雨带]]和[[外流_(气象学)|外流]]有所增长<ref name="disc1">{{cite report | author = Stacy R. Stewart | date = 2014-08-22 | title = Tropical Depression Thirteen-E Discussion Number 1 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep13/ep132014.discus.001.shtml | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006092257/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep13/ep132014.discus.001.shtml | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2014-10-06 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，美国国家飓风中心于8月22日清晨将位于墨西哥[[阿卡普尔科|阿卡普尔科]]东南偏南方向约595公里的系统归类为第十三{{lang|en|E}}号热带低气压。[[美国南部|美国南部]]上空的强烈[[高压脊|高压脊]]逐渐向墨西哥北部扩张，受其影响，系统在处[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]阶段时总体保持向[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]方向移动。<ref name="TCR" />
{{Most intense Pacific hurricanes|align=right}}
外界环境有利于低气压强化，[[热带气旋预测模型|热带气旋预测模型]]在系统还只是热带低气压时就预料气旋会达到[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的四级飓风强度<ref name="disc1" />。成为热带低气压仅6小时后，美国国家飓风中心就将系统升级成热带风暴并以“玛丽”（{{lang|en|Marie}}）命名，这也是[[2014年太平洋飓风季|2014年太平洋飓风季]]第13场获得命名的风暴<ref>{{cite report | author = Robbie J. Berg | date = 2014-08-22 | title = Tropical Storm Marie Discussion Number 2 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140904182149/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep13/ep132014.discus.002.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep13/ep132014.discus.002.shtml | location = Miami, Florida | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-09-04}}</ref>。由于[[海面温度|水温]]较高，[[风切变|风切变]]很少，气旋迅速组织，发展出由强烈对流组成的[[中心密集云区|中心密集云区]]<ref>{{cite report | author = Todd B. Kimberlain | date = 2014-08-23 | title = Tropical Storm Marie Discussion Number 4 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | archivedate = 2014-11-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep13/ep132014.discus.005.shtml | location = Miami, Florida | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141103003215/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep13/ep132014.discus.005.shtml}}</ref>。8月23日，美国国家飓风中心将玛丽升级成飓风<ref>{{cite report | author = David P. Roberts | date = 2014-08-23 | title = Hurricane Marie Discussion Number 6 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep13/ep132014.discus.006.shtml | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2014-10-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006111817/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep13/ep132014.discus.006.shtml}}</ref>，气旋还于当晚开始形成[[风眼|风眼]]<ref>{{cite report | author = Christopher W. Landsea | date = 2014-08-23 | title = Hurricane Marie Discussion Number 8 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep13/ep132014.discus.008.shtml | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141103003122/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep13/ep132014.discus.008.shtml | deadurl = no | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2014-11-03}}</ref>。次日风暴仍在[[快速增强|迅速强化]]，其风眼变得更加清晰，周围有强烈的风眼墙围绕<ref>{{cite report | author = John P. Cangialosi | date = 2014-08-24 | title = Hurricane Marie Discussion Number 10 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006152306/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep13/ep132014.discus.010.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep13/ep132014.discus.010.shtml | archivedate = 2014-10-06 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。玛丽在此期间转朝正西方向移动了一段时间，然后恢复到原有前进方向。8月24日下午18点，气旋达到[[五级太平洋飓风列表|五级飓风]]强度，成为继[[2010年太平洋飓风季|2010年]]的[[2010年飓风西莉亚|飓风西莉亚]]以来首场五级[[太平洋飓风|太平洋飓风]]<ref name="TCR" />。美国国家飓风中心热带分析和预测处，以及卫星分析处通过[[德沃夏克分析法|德沃夏克分析法]]对玛丽进行分析后得到的评分为7，据此估算其[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]达到每小时260公里，最低[[气压|气压]]低至918[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，27.11[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]），成为1949年开始有纪录以来，[[国际日期变更线|国际日期变更线]]以东太平洋形成的第7强飓风<ref name="TCR" /><ref name="EPAC HURDAT" />{{#tag:ref|虽然玛丽的强度在有纪录以来的所有太平洋飓风中可以排到第7位，但要从1988年起，相应纪录才属于可靠纪录<ref name="TCR" />。|group="注"|name="TCR"}}。仅仅三周后，[[飓风奥迪尔|飓风奥迪尔]]也达到了同样的气压低值，与玛丽并列成为有史以来的第7强太平洋飓风<ref>{{cite report | author = John P. Cangialosi and Todd B. Kimberlain | work = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141222101849/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP152014_Odile.pdf | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2014-12-19 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Tropical Cyclone Report: Hurricane Odile | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP152014_Odile.pdf | format = PDF | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2014-12-22 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。达到最高强度时，玛丽的规模非常庞大，其热带风暴强度风场有925公里宽<ref name="TCR" /><ref>{{cite web | author = Hurricane Research Division | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2014-08-29 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Hurricane Marie Operational Best Track | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150503055301/http://www.ral.ucar.edu/guidance/realtime/plots/northeastpacific/2014/ep132014/bep132014.dat | url = http://www.ral.ucar.edu/guidance/realtime/plots/northeastpacific/2014/ep132014/bep132014.dat | archivedate = 2015-05-03 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

达到最高强度后不久，玛丽进入[[眼墙置换|眼墙置换周期]]，有外层风眼形成，对流也相应减弱<ref>{{cite report | author = Todd B. Kimberlain | date = 2014-08-25 | title = Hurricane Marie Discussion Number 13 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006103018/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep13/ep132014.discus.013.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep13/ep132014.discus.013.shtml | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2014-10-06}}</ref>，这一减弱过程也受到逐渐降低的水温推动。到了8月26日清晨，风眼与之前相比已模糊了很多<ref>{{cite report | author = Todd B. Kimberlain | date = 2014-08-26 | title = Hurricane Marie Discussion Number 17 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep13/ep132014.discus.017.shtml | location = Miami, Florida | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006121125/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep13/ep132014.discus.017.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-10-06}}</ref>。飓风中双层风眼特征持续了一整天，但外围风眼墙因雷暴进一步减弱而出现缺口<ref>{{cite report | author = John P. Cangialosi | date = 2014-08-26 | title = Hurricane Marie Discussion Number 18 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep13/ep132014.discus.018.shtml | location = Miami, Florida | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006145012/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep13/ep132014.discus.018.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-10-06}}</ref>。8月27日晚上，玛丽已降至热带风暴强度，这时[[大气环流|环流]]已经从对流中暴露出来<ref>{{cite report | author = Daniel P. Brown | date = 2014-08-27 | title = Tropical Storm Marie Discussion Number 24 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006075235/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep13/ep132014.discus.024.shtml | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep13/ep132014.discus.024.shtml | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2014-10-06}}</ref>。受[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]]附近逐渐增强的高压脊影响，风暴加速向西北偏西移动，进入的海域水温更低，并且空气也更干燥<ref>{{cite report | author = Robbie J. Berg | date = 2014-08-28 | title = Tropical Storm Marie Discussion Number 25 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep13/ep132014.discus.025.shtml | location = Miami, Florida | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006164917/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep13/ep132014.discus.025.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-10-06}}</ref>。由于没能产生更多对流，玛丽于8月28日晚退化成残留低气压<ref name="TCR" />。系统继续向西北方向前进，残余环流逐渐收紧。8月29日，系统继续产生烈风强度大风<ref name="TCR" /><ref>{{cite report | author = Scott Stripling | work = Tropical Analysis Forecast Branch; National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2014-08-30 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140907171950/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDEP/2014/TWDEP.201408300232.txt | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDEP/2014/TWDEP.201408300232.txt | location = Miami, Florida | format = TXT | archivedate = 2014-09-07 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。受弱东向气流影响，玛丽的残留转向西进，之后又转向西南偏西，缓慢进入太平洋开放水域，虽然强度很弱，但覆盖范围仍然广阔。最终，系统失去了原本层次分明的中心，于9月2日在[[夏威夷州|夏威夷州]]东北方向约1950公里洋面完全消散。<ref name="TCR" />

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
=== 墨西哥 ===
[[File:Wedge_Video_D_Ramey_Logan.ogv|thumb]]带去的大型涌浪]]

飓风玛丽的核心部分一直远离海岸，但[[格雷罗州|格雷罗州]]和[[瓦哈卡州|瓦哈卡州]]还是收到了“绿色”预警信号，[[哈利斯科州|哈利斯科州]]、[[科利马州|科利马州]]、[[米却肯州|米却肯州]]和[[恰帕斯州|恰帕斯州]]收到“蓝色”（最低）预警信号<ref>{{cite news | title = Activan alertas 6 estados por Marie; prevén que sea huracán | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | date = 2014-08-22 | newspaper = El Universal | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140826113506/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2014/activan-alertas-verde-y-azul-en-6-estados-por-39marie-39-1032317.html | archivedate = 2014-08-26 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2014/activan-alertas-verde-y-azul-en-6-estados-por-39marie-39-1032317.html}}</ref>。瓦哈卡州出现暴雨，引发洪灾和山体滑坡，其中又以沿海的[[胡基拉区|胡基拉区]]（{{lang|en|Juquila District}}）和[[波丘特拉区|波丘特拉区]]（{{lang|en|Pochutla District}}）所受影响最为严重<ref name="Missing">{{cite web | work = [[埃菲通讯社|Agencia EFE, S.A.]] | publisher = El Heraldo | date = 2014-08-25 | accessdate = 2014-05-03 | title = Huracán "Marie" deja 10.000 familias damnificadas y tres desaparecidos | archivedate = 2014-10-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141024025419/http://www.elheraldo.co/internacional/huracan-marie-deja-10000-familias-damnificadas-y-tres-desaparecidos-164009 | url = http://www.elheraldo.co/internacional/huracan-marie-deja-10000-familias-damnificadas-y-tres-desaparecidos-164009}}</ref>。有5人被暴涨的河水卷走，之后获救时均已受伤。墨西哥200号联邦公路部分路段及一座桥梁被迫封闭<ref>{{cite news | title = Marie causa daños en carreteras de Oaxaca | url = http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2014/marie-causa-danios-en-carreteras-de-oaxaca-1032518.html | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | date = 2014-08-22 | newspaper = El Universal | archivedate = 2014-08-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140828200654/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2014/marie-causa-danios-en-carreteras-de-oaxaca-1032518.html | deadurl = no}}</ref>。约有1万户家庭流离失所，瓦哈卡州要求宣示为灾区以获取联邦援助<ref>{{cite web | publisher = ABC | date = 2014-08-25 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Alerta en México por fuertes lluvias asociadas al paso del huracán Marie | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150503073218/http://agencias.abc.es/agencias/noticia.asp?noticia=1652968 | deadurl = yes | url = http://agencias.abc.es/agencias/noticia.asp?noticia=1652968 | archivedate = 2015-05-03 }}</ref>。科利马州有4幢建筑物被[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]{{#tag:ref|[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]指平均潮汐高度和风暴产生潮汐高度之间的差距<ref name="gloss" />。|group="注"}}摧毁，另有10幢受损<ref>{{cite web | newspaper = El Universal | author = NOTIMEX | date = 2014-08-26 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Marejadas dañan nuevamente balnearios de Colima | archivedate = 2014-08-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140829122417/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2014/marejadas-balnearios-colima-1033261.html | url = http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2014/marejadas-balnearios-colima-1033261.html | deadurl = no}}</ref>。马拉巴斯科河（{{lang|en|Marabasco River}}）与圣尼古拉斯河（{{lang|en|San Nicolás River}}）沿线有两人因洪灾遇难<ref name="Jalisco deaths">{{cite web|author=Antonio Vázquez López |publisher=Notisistema |date=2014-08-25 |accessdate=2015-05-03 |title=Marie causa la muerte de dos personas en la Costalegre de Jalisco |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141023224117/http://www.notisistema.com/noticias/marie-causa-la-muerte-de-dos-personas-en-la-costalegre-de-jalisco/ |archivedate=2014-10-23 |url=http://www.notisistema.com/noticias/marie-causa-la-muerte-de-dos-personas-en-la-costalegre-de-jalisco/ }}</ref>。阿卡普尔科附近和科利马州也出现轻度洪灾，其中科利马州海岸还受到4.9米的大浪冲击<ref>{{cite news | title = Marie ya es huracán; no tocará tierra: SMN | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | date = 2014-08-22 | newspaper = El Universal | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140830090537/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2014/impreso/-8216marie-8217-ya-es-huracan-no-tocara-tierra-smn-95881.html | archivedate = 2014-08-30 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2014/impreso/-8216marie-8217-ya-es-huracan-no-tocara-tierra-smn-95881.html}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Guerrero descarta daños graves por huracán Marie | archivedate = 2014-10-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141023221711/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2014/guerrero-lluvias-marie-1032953.html | url = http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2014/guerrero-lluvias-marie-1032953.html | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | date = 2014-08-25 | newspaper = El Universal | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | publisher = teleSUR | date = 2014-08-24 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Hurricane Marie Causes Damages in Colima, Mexico | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150215231137/http://www.telesurtv.net/english/news/Hurricane-Marie-Causes-Damages-in-Colima-Mexico--20140824-0047.html | archivedate = 2015-02-13 | url = http://www.telesurtv.net/english/news/Hurricane-Marie-Causes-Damages-in-Colima-Mexico--20140824-0047.html}}</ref>。[[瓜达拉哈拉_(墨西哥)|瓜达拉哈拉]]有许多树木倒塌，12家商店关闭<ref>{{cite news | title = Marie se aleja de Jalisco sin causar mayores daños | url = http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2014/jalisco-marie-lluvia-1032987.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140827112158/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2014/jalisco-marie-lluvia-1032987.html | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | date = 2014-08-25 | newspaper = El Universal | archivedate = 2014-08-27 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

8月25日，[[南下加利福尼亚州|南下加利福尼亚州]]的[[洛斯卡沃斯|洛斯卡沃斯]]近海一艘载有7人的渔船因遭遇大型卷浪而倾覆。船上4人成功游回岸边，但另外3人仍然下落不明，推定已经死亡。<ref name="TCR" /><ref name="Missing" />飓风玛丽外围边缘的强劲[[雨带|雨带]]在该州部分地区产生倾盆大雨。[[洛斯卡沃斯|洛斯卡沃斯]]附近有多条道路因山体滑坡阻塞，阵风还刮倒了许多树木，导致多条输电线缆中断。由于情况危险，洛斯卡沃斯的所有学校都在8月25日停课。<ref>{{cite web | newspaper = Zócalo Saltillo | date = 2014-08-25 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Suspenden clases en Los Cabos por huracán Marie | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141023215150/http://www.zocalo.com.mx/seccion/articulo/suspenden-clases-en-los-cabos-por-huracan-marie-1408979461 | archivedate = 2014-10-23 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.zocalo.com.mx/seccion/articulo/suspenden-clases-en-los-cabos-por-huracan-marie-1408979461}}</ref>

=== 美国 ===
[[File:Long_Beach,_California_Middle_Breakwater_damage_from_Hurricane_Marie_2014.jpg|thumb]]的防浪堤被突破]]

考虑到玛丽的庞大规模，气象机构预计其北面很远地区的拍岸浪高度也会上升。加利福尼亚[[大洛杉矶地区|大洛杉矶地区]]收到[[美国恶劣天气术语|大浪公告]]。[[美国国家气象局|美国国家气象局]]驻地方办事处警告[[洛杉矶县|洛杉矶县]]和[[文图拉县|文图拉县]]居民，他们“有可能会看到近年来飓风产生的最大海浪。”<ref name="NWSwarn1" />气象机构预计浪高会达到3到4.6米，还有可能出现沿海洪灾和结构性破坏。[[橙县_(加利福尼亚州)|橙县]]和[[圣巴巴拉县_(加利福尼亚州)|圣巴巴拉县]]也有收到公告<ref name="NWSwarn1">{{cite report | work = National Weather Service in Los Angeles, California | publisher = Iowa Environmental Mesonet National Weather Service | date = 2014-08-24 | title = Severe Weather Statement: High Surf Advisory}}</ref><ref>{{cite report | work = National Weather Service in San Diego, California | publisher = Iowa Environmental Mesonet National Weather Service | date = 2014-08-25 | title = Severe Weather Statement: High Surf Advisory}}</ref>。这些地区朝向南面的的海岸最终出现了高达6.1米的巨浪，但朝向西面的海岸则只有2.4米<ref name="DBAug28">{{cite web | author = Sandy Mazza | newspaper = Daily Breeze | date = 2014-08-28 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Catalina Island digging out from Hurricane Marie winds, swells | url = http://www.dailybreeze.com/general-news/20140828/catalina-island-digging-out-from-hurricane-marie-winds-swells | archivedate = 2014-10-23 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141023224950/http://www.dailybreeze.com/general-news/20140828/catalina-island-digging-out-from-hurricane-marie-winds-swells}}</ref>。

大浪和高涨的海潮共同影响，再加上从南到北的强烈[[沿岸流|沿岸流]]因[[洛斯维第斯|洛斯维第斯半岛]]地形而受到阻碍，[[海豹滩_(加利福尼亚州)|海豹滩]]因此遭受了严重的沿海洪灾。有4个街区的海滨财物受到影响，多幢公寓一楼的积水有好几英寸深。<ref name="Cali1">{{cite web | work = Associated Press | publisher = The Weather Channel | date = 2014-08-28 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Hurricane Marie's Wave Action Floods Seal Beach, California | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150425032000/http://www.weather.com/storms/hurricane/news/flooding-inundates-southern-california-beach-town-20140827 | archivedate = 2015-04-25 | url = http://www.weather.com/storms/hurricane/news/flooding-inundates-southern-california-beach-town-20140827}}</ref>强烈的[[海岸侵蚀|海滩侵蚀]]导致7600至15200立方米沙子流失，当地因此进入[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]来协助恢复工作<ref>{{cite web | newspaper = Orange County Breeze | date = 2014-09-04 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Seal Beach works with County of Orange to replace sand lost to Hurricane Marie | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141023224950/http://www.dailybreeze.com/general-news/20140828/catalina-island-digging-out-from-hurricane-marie-winds-swells | archivedate = 2014-10-23 | url = http://www.oc-breeze.com/2014/09/04/58179_seal-beach-works-with-county-of-orange-to-replace-sand-lost-to-hurricane-marie/ }}</ref>。[[马利布_(加利福尼亚州)|马利布码头]]附近有许多冲浪者被强烈的涌浪冲得撞在一起，其中一人撞到石头上后晕倒并淹死<ref>{{cite web | author = Emily Sawicki | newspaper = Malibu Times | date = 2014-08-26 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Surfer Dies After Drowning Near Malibu Pier | url = http://www.malibutimes.com/news/article_50cc2c42-2d57-11e4-9789-0019bb2963f4.html | archivedate = 2014-08-31 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140831064010/http://www.malibutimes.com/news/article_50cc2c42-2d57-11e4-9789-0019bb2963f4.html}}</ref>。马利布码头本身也受到一定程度破坏，一间建于20世纪50年代、供救生员使用的房屋被毁<ref>{{cite web | author = Samia Khan | newspaper = NBC Los Angeles | date = 2014-08-28 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = High Surf Advisory Continues After Waves Destroy Lifeguard Building, Damage Malibu Pier | archivedate = 2014-10-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141012130146/http://www.nbclosangeles.com/news/local/High-Surf-Advisory-Continues-Waves-Destroy-Lifeguard-Building-Damages-Malibu-Pier-273018501.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nbclosangeles.com/news/local/High-Surf-Advisory-Continues-Waves-Destroy-Lifeguard-Building-Damages-Malibu-Pier-273018501.html}}</ref>。马利布以北还有一幢建筑物塌入海中<ref name="LATMalibu">{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150328091645/http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-lanow-catalina-damage-hurricane-marie-waves-20140828-story.html | newspaper = Los Angeles Times | date = 2014-08-28 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Catalina Island suffers significant damage from Hurricane Marie waves | archivedate = 2015-03-28 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-lanow-catalina-damage-hurricane-marie-waves-20140828-story.html}}</ref>。[[洛杉矶县消防局|洛杉矶县消防局]]在8月26日一共进行了超过115起海上救援<ref>{{cite web | newspaper = 89.3 KPCC | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141011123040/http://www.scpr.org/news/2014/08/27/46310/california-beach-town-sees-flooding-from-hurricane/ | date = 2014-08-27 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = High surf: Seal Beach floods, Malibu Pier closed, 100+ rescued (updated) | archivedate = 2014-10-11 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.scpr.org/news/2014/08/27/46310/california-beach-town-sees-flooding-from-hurricane/}}</ref>。次日又进行了超过170次，其中73次是在[[纽波特比奇_(加利福尼亚州)|纽波特比奇]][[巴尔博亚半岛|巴尔博亚半岛]]最东端的冲浪胜地“The Wedge”（意为“楔子”）<ref>{{cite web | author = Andrew Lopez | newspaper = NBC Los Angeles | date = 2014-08-28 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Large Crowds Expected Again as High Surf Pounds Orange County Beaches | archivedate = 2014-10-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141024015312/http://www.nbclosangeles.com/news/local/Large-Crowds-Expected-Again-as-High-Surf-Pounds-Orange-County-Beaches-Wedge-Waves-273069711.html | url = http://www.nbclosangeles.com/news/local/Large-Crowds-Expected-Again-as-High-Surf-Pounds-Orange-County-Beaches-Wedge-Waves-273069711.html}}</ref>。
[[File:Hurricane_Marie_Middle_Breakwater_repair.JPG|thumb]]

[[长滩_(加利福尼亚州)|长滩]]港及周边也出现严重洪灾<ref name="Cali1" />。[[美国陆军工兵队|美国陆军工兵队]]被派往当地检查中部[[防浪堤|防浪堤]]受到的严重破坏<ref name="Breakwater1">{{cite web | author = Karen Robes Meeks | newspaper = Long Beach Press Telegram | date = 2014-09-04 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Army Corps of Engineers examines Hurricane Marie surge damage to Long Beach breakwater | url = http://www.presstelegram.com/general-news/20140903/army-corps-of-engineers-examines-hurricane-marie-surge-damage-to-long-beach-breakwater | location = Long Beach, California | archivedate = 2014-10-23 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141023221132/http://www.presstelegram.com/general-news/20140903/army-corps-of-engineers-examines-hurricane-marie-surge-damage-to-long-beach-breakwater}}</ref>。共有11段防浪堤严重受损，其中3处完全被掏空<ref name="Breakwater2">{{cite web | author = Jonathan Van Dyke | newspaper = The Grunion Gazettes | date = 2014-09-10 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Update: First Breakwater Fixes Estimated To Cost $20 Million | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140914125118/http://www.gazettes.com/news/update-first-breakwater-fixes-estimated-to-cost-million/article_99922b48-3527-11e4-9e5c-001a4bcf887a.html | archivedate = 2014-09-14 | url = http://www.gazettes.com/news/update-first-breakwater-fixes-estimated-to-cost-million/article_99922b48-3527-11e4-9e5c-001a4bcf887a.html}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | author = Jonathan Van Dyke | newspaper = The Grunion Gazettes | date = 2014-09-05 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Army Corps Works To Solve Breakwater Breaches After Storm Surge | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140907134300/http://www.gazettes.com/news/army-corps-works-to-solve-breakwater-breaches-after-storm-surge/article_99922b48-3527-11e4-9e5c-001a4bcf887a.html | archivedate = 2014-09-07 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.gazettes.com/news/army-corps-works-to-solve-breakwater-breaches-after-storm-surge/article_99922b48-3527-11e4-9e5c-001a4bcf887a.html}}</ref>。防浪堤全长5600米<ref>{{cite web | author = Veronica Rocha | newspaper = Los Angeles Times | date = 2014-09-10 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Hurricane swells cause $20 million in damage to port breakwater | url = http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-long-beach-breakwater-damage-hurricane-marie-20140910-story.html | archivedate = 2015-03-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150322062409/http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-long-beach-breakwater-damage-hurricane-marie-20140910-story.html}}</ref>，其中有470米严重受损，260米基本被毁，另有526米受到中等程度破坏<ref name="BreakwaterJan1">{{cite web | author = Karen Robes Meeks | newspaper = Long Beach Press Telegram | date = 2015-01-10 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Port of Long Beach may spend $3.8M more to fix Hurricane Marie damage | url = http://www.presstelegram.com/business/20150110/port-of-long-beach-may-spend-38m-more-to-fix-hurricane-marie-damage | location = Long Beach, California | archivedate = 2015-02-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150212191750/http://www.presstelegram.com/business/20150110/port-of-long-beach-may-spend-38m-more-to-fix-hurricane-marie-damage}}</ref>。估计风暴刮倒的岩石有数百吨之多。附近的[[圣佩德罗_(洛杉矶)|圣佩德罗]]（{{lang|en|San Pedro}}）和长滩的防浪堤也受到重创，只是程度不及中部防浪堤严重<ref name="Breakwater2" />。[[海上发射公司|海上发射公司]][[海上发射公司装配指挥船|装配指挥船]]附近的一条巷道因防浪堤破损产生的碎石而受损<ref name="Breakwater1" />。附近的码头因防浪堤受损而遭受了价值约300万美元的破坏<ref name="BreakwaterJan2">{{cite web | author = Karen Robes Meeks | newspaper = Long Beach Press Telegram | date = 2015-01-12 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Port of Long Beach leaders approve $3.8 million to fix Hurricane Marie-damaged port areas | location = Long Beach, California | archivedate = 2015-02-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150212191147/http://www.presstelegram.com/business/20150112/port-of-long-beach-leaders-approve-38-million-to-fix-hurricane-marie-damaged-port-areas | url = http://www.presstelegram.com/business/20150112/port-of-long-beach-leaders-approve-38-million-to-fix-hurricane-marie-damaged-port-areas}}</ref>。汹涌的海浪将两艘[[驳船|驳船]]和一般游艇从系锚上扯下，只能之后再拖回岸边。有两个码头因作业环境太过危险而关闭。<ref name="PTAug28">{{cite web | author = Greg Yee | newspaper = Long Beach Press Telegram | date = 2014-08-28 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Wednesday’s high surf brings flooding, ocean rescues, traffic | archivedate = 2015-02-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150212223642/http://www.presstelegram.com/general-news/20140827/wednesdays-high-surf-brings-flooding-ocean-rescues-traffic | url = http://www.presstelegram.com/general-news/20140827/wednesdays-high-surf-brings-flooding-ocean-rescues-traffic}}</ref>飓风玛丽过去不到两周后，[[2014年飓风诺伯特|飓风诺伯特]]又对这片地区构成威胁，这时防浪堤尚未修复，只能用大规模沙质护堤加固，当地居民还获得了沙袋作为防灾物资<ref>{{cite web | author1 = Hetty Chang | newspaper = NBC Los Angeles | date = 2014-09-06 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Residents Brace for Hurricane Norbert | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141023222534/http://www.nbclosangeles.com/news/local/Residents-Brace-for-Hurricane-Norbert-274196171.html | url = http://www.nbclosangeles.com/news/local/Residents-Brace-for-Hurricane-Norbert-274196171.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-10-23 | author2 = Jane Yamamoto}}</ref>。美国陆军工兵队估计，单是修复中部防浪堤上破坏较大的部分就要花费至少2000万美元<ref name="Breakwater2" />。9月18日，康诺利太平洋有限公司签订了修复防浪堤的合约，建设工作于10月8日开始。估计整个项目需要使用2至3万吨岩石<ref>{{cite web | author = Greg Fuderer | publisher = United States Army Corps of Engineers | date = 2014-11-03 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Port breakwater repairs underway | location = Long Beach, California | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150212200547/http://www.spl.usace.army.mil/Media/NewsStories/tabid/1318/Article/547743/port-breakwater-repairs-underway.aspx | archivedate = 2015-02-12 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.spl.usace.army.mil/Media/NewsStories/tabid/1318/Article/547743/port-breakwater-repairs-underway.aspx}}</ref>。包括{{lang|en|F}}码头、{{lang|en|J}}南码头和海军摩尔路在内的海军摩尔周边地区起初获得了20万美元的维修预算，2015年1月，长滩海港专员委员会将这个数字大幅提升到400万美元<ref name="BreakwaterJan2" />。

[[圣卡塔利娜岛|圣卡塔利娜岛]]有许多重量估计达到1400公斤的巨石被海浪冲到内陆，阿瓦隆港受到重创，许多停在船坞里的船都被推翻<ref name="Cali1" />。港口内连续数日都四处散落着各种碎屑，其中最多的是木材的碎片。怀特港的一处码头也部分被毁<ref>{{cite web | author = Robert J. Lopez | newspaper = Los Angeles Times | date = 2014-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150313181448/http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-waves-damage-catalina-island-hurricane-marie-20140827-story.html | archivedate = 2015-03-13 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Big surf pounds Catalina, causes major damage to boatyard, harbor | url = http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-waves-damage-catalina-island-hurricane-marie-20140827-story.html}}</ref>。海滩上一艘7.6米长的船被冲入岛上名为“卡塔利娜”（{{lang|en|Catalina}}）的唯一一家洗衣店。这间店铺和附近的船厂都完全被毁<ref>{{cite web | author = Hetty Chang and Kelly Goff | newspaper = NBC Los Angeles | date = 2014-08-28 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Catalina Residents Clean Up After the Storm | archivedate = 2014-10-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141023222820/http://www.nbclosangeles.com/news/local/Catalina-Residents-Clean-Up-After-the-Storm-273115191.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nbclosangeles.com/news/local/Catalina-Residents-Clean-Up-After-the-Storm-273115191.html}}</ref>。据报道称，岛上海滩所受到的破坏程度是继[[1997年太平洋飓风季|1997年9月]]的[[1997年飓风琳达|飓风琳达]]以来最严重的<ref name="LATMalibu" /><ref>{{cite report | author = Max Mayfield | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 1997-10-25 | accessdate = 2015-05-03 | title = Preliminary Report: Hurricane Linda | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/1997linda.html | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2014-11-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141102192752/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/1997linda.html | deadurl = no}}</ref>。卡塔利娜快速渡轮于8月27日因海况恶劣中止服务<ref name="PTAug28" />。估计整个圣卡塔利娜岛一共遭受了300到500万美元的损失<ref name="DBAug28" />。整个加利福尼亚州的损失数额则有近2000万美元<ref name="TCR" />。

